<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=158dde820051fe69376e2cbb4a39c15c sig_cn_org=f5a1418ba8e38291a481b8edf14736f1 source=17.5 
     <para>
      Fix <command>MERGE</command> into a partitioned table
      with <literal>DO NOTHING</literal> actions (Tender Wang)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;25303678a">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      将<command>MERGE</command>应用到带有<literal>DO NOTHING</literal>操作的分区表中（Tender Wang）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;25303678a">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=158dde820051fe69376e2cbb4a39c15c -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=f9a7ffe324221e74ddd2c48c6be607bc sig_cn_org=de6b54b87b2c9e0b8fb25f977690dc5d source=17.5 
     <para>
      Some cases failed with <quote>unknown action in MERGE WHEN
      clause</quote> errors.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      一些情况因<quote>MERGE WHEN子句中的未知操作</quote>错误而失败。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=f9a7ffe324221e74ddd2c48c6be607bc -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
Author: Tom Lane <tgl@sss.pgh.pa.us>
Branch: master [7c8728494] 2025-04-15 12:08:34 -0400
Branch: REL_17_STABLE [3c39c000c] 2025-04-15 12:08:34 -0400
Branch: REL_16_STABLE [f04e0faa3] 2025-04-15 12:08:34 -0400
Branch: REL_15_STABLE [97d671672] 2025-04-15 12:08:34 -0400
Branch: REL_14_STABLE [4604928ed] 2025-04-15 12:08:34 -0400
-->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=5731813aa24538ccbdd14a7ef2c1ad92 sig_cn_org=b13d0e1ef05cefe7eb962d42736feae3 source=17.5 
     <para>
      Prevent failure in <command>INSERT</command> commands when the table
      has a <literal>GENERATED</literal> column of a domain data type and
      the domain's constraints disallow null values (Jian He)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;3c39c000c">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      防止在表中具有域数据类型的<literal>GENERATED</literal>列且域的约束不允许空值时，
      <command>INSERT</command>命令失败（贾恩·何）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;3c39c000c">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=5731813aa24538ccbdd14a7ef2c1ad92 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=d080e162c87edbe30c62078e0f112c8c sig_cn_org=84cb7baa4289987ee04c6f7595166a86 source=17.5 
     <para>
      Constraint failure was reported even if the generation expression
      produced a perfectly okay result.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      即使生成表达式产生了完全正确的结果，也会报告约束失败。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=d080e162c87edbe30c62078e0f112c8c -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
Author: Tom Lane <tgl@sss.pgh.pa.us>
Branch: master [691836405] 2025-04-05 15:01:48 -0400
Branch: REL_17_STABLE [5e7be43f4] 2025-04-05 15:01:33 -0400
Branch: REL_16_STABLE [1980ec2bc] 2025-04-05 15:01:33 -0400
Branch: REL_15_STABLE [ede29a1e4] 2025-04-05 15:01:33 -0400
Branch: REL_14_STABLE [754a3d82d] 2025-04-05 15:01:33 -0400
Branch: REL_13_STABLE [e276b5829] 2025-04-05 15:01:33 -0400
-->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=69bd815df65ca596f9163d341f0da1a8 sig_cn_org=f10b9161043685a98e37ff1846849885 source=17.5 
     <para>
      Correctly process references to outer CTE names that appear within
      a <literal>WITH</literal> clause attached to
      an <command>INSERT</command>/<command>UPDATE</command>/<command>DELETE</command>/<command>MERGE</command>
      command that's inside <literal>WITH</literal> (Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;5e7be43f4">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      正确处理出现在附加于
      <literal>WITH</literal>子句中的外部CTE名称的引用，
      该子句附属于位于<literal>WITH</literal>内的
      <command>INSERT</command>/<command>UPDATE</command>/<command>DELETE</command>/<command>MERGE</command>
      命令（Tom Lane）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;5e7be43f4">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=69bd815df65ca596f9163d341f0da1a8 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=04ed02b78598d642637011c1877bff07 sig_cn_org=4f8147344d657fc795f69f7138437d01 source=17.5 
     <para>
      The parser failed to detect disallowed recursion cases, nor did it
      account for such references when sorting CTEs into a usable order.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      解析器未能检测到不允许的递归情况，也未在对CTE进行可用顺序排序时考虑此类引用。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=04ed02b78598d642637011c1877bff07 -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
Author: Amit Langote <amitlan@postgresql.org>
Branch: master [d4f79865d] 2025-03-13 09:56:36 +0900
Branch: REL_17_STABLE [8b2392ae3] 2025-03-13 09:56:49 +0900
-->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=0315e8bba3a792f27914724089c0be5f sig_cn_org=411bf35d89bc6eedfec3fd2007dd52ee source=17.5 
     <para>
      Fix misprocessing of casts within the keys of JSON constructor
      expressions (Amit Langote)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8b2392ae3">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复了在 JSON 构造函数表达式的键中对类型转换的错误处理（Amit Langote）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8b2392ae3">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=0315e8bba3a792f27914724089c0be5f -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
