<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=40fa49980c699eadadb793b924cd8c47 sig_cn_org=efe8bafff4b9c01d02b24cae0fb6760a source=17.5 
     <para>
      Don't try to parallelize <function>array_agg()</function> when the
      argument is of an anonymous record type (Richard Guo, Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;43847dd5e">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      不要尝试对参数为匿名记录类型的<function>array_agg()</function>进行并行化（Richard Guo, Tom Lane）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;43847dd5e">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=40fa49980c699eadadb793b924cd8c47 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=2abf02519eb80855c74c21d1d115f0ab sig_cn_org=b8cdde12e7837d0f220a4566bd870910 source=17.5 
     <para>
      The protocol for communicating with parallel workers doesn't support
      identifying the concrete record type that a worker is returning.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      与并行工作者通信的协议不支持识别工作者返回的具体记录类型。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=2abf02519eb80855c74c21d1d115f0ab -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
