<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=99cefb95d6c1831099ae3b5e57ebb02d sig_cn_org=b26f24c23dcf7b165c3ebaf8843b31d5 source=17.5 
     <para>
      Fix <literal>ALTER TABLE ADD COLUMN</literal> to correctly handle
      the case of a domain type that has a default
      (Jian He, Tom Lane, Tender Wang)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d6dd2a02b">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;0941aadcd">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复 <literal>ALTER TABLE ADD COLUMN</literal> 以正确处理
      具有默认值的域类型的情况
      （贾恩·何，汤姆·莱恩，Tender Wang）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d6dd2a02b">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;0941aadcd">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=99cefb95d6c1831099ae3b5e57ebb02d -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=354fad85ad3fdf150815daa8a271f7dc sig_cn_org=f4c33efea18c022c9ad1b1b7ab82d110 source=17.5 
     <para>
      If a domain type has a default, adding a column of that type (without
      any explicit <literal>DEFAULT</literal>
      clause) failed to install the domain's default
      value in existing rows, instead leaving the new column null.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      如果域类型有默认值，添加该类型的列（没有任何显式的<literal>DEFAULT</literal>
      子句）会导致无法在现有行中安装域的默认值，而是将新列置为空。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=354fad85ad3fdf150815daa8a271f7dc -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
