<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=4821d740f9bfd73da1fe8561881e708d sig_cn_org=1f15a6cbbdb9931984bb65b6484ed272 source=17.5 
     <para>
      Respond to interrupts (such as query cancel) while waiting for
      asynchronous subplans of an Append plan node (Heikki Linnakangas)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;e731e9d5e">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      在等待Append计划节点的异步子计划时响应中断（例如查询取消）（Heikki Linnakangas）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;e731e9d5e">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=4821d740f9bfd73da1fe8561881e708d -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=0bd9d17379349a61c241ca3ba7d03e3a sig_cn_org=add8e5016a3ed83ae249bf3537473210 source=17.5 
     <para>
      Previously, nothing would happen until one of the subplans becomes
      ready.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      之前，直到其中一个子计划准备好之前，什么都不会发生。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=0bd9d17379349a61c241ca3ba7d03e3a -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
Author: Michael Paquier <michael@paquier.xyz>
Branch: master [039549d70] 2025-04-08 07:57:19 +0900
Branch: REL_17_STABLE [5cbbe70a9] 2025-04-08 07:58:47 +0900
Branch: REL_16_STABLE [e2a82cd23] 2025-04-08 07:58:50 +0900
-->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=0d53040cc3147656fbbb560e8d69b94b sig_cn_org=b950b3c8aa0911ac33007248694dfa48 source=17.5 
     <para>
      Report the I/O statistics of active WAL senders more frequently
      (Bertrand Drouvot)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;5cbbe70a9">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      更频繁地报告活动 WAL 发送者的 I/O 统计信息（Bertrand Drouvot）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;5cbbe70a9">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=0d53040cc3147656fbbb560e8d69b94b -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=f4499469434d486b4aa42d88f08d30fc sig_cn_org=07be0111e41917e8793fa70af7fcbadd source=17.5 
     <para>
      Previously, the <structname>pg_stat_io</structname> view failed to
      accumulate I/O performed by a WAL sender until that process exited.
      Now such I/O will be reported after at most one second's delay.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      之前，<structname>pg_stat_io</structname> 视图未能累计 WAL 发送进程退出前执行的 I/O。
      现在此类 I/O 最多延迟一秒后即可报告。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=f4499469434d486b4aa42d88f08d30fc -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
Author: Michael Paquier <michael@paquier.xyz>
Branch: master [2e5779083] 2025-04-11 10:00:21 +0900
Branch: REL_17_STABLE [3339847cc] 2025-04-11 10:02:15 +0900
Branch: REL_16_STABLE [c922ae2c4] 2025-04-11 10:02:17 +0900
Branch: REL_15_STABLE [ec59500a1] 2025-04-11 10:02:18 +0900
Branch: REL_14_STABLE [873aff945] 2025-04-11 10:02:20 +0900
Branch: REL_13_STABLE [e2f42f812] 2025-04-11 10:02:21 +0900
-->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=03eb6141e6353f8a39e5919d1f8287d4 sig_cn_org=a9c0545ab8e5e93b315daec21a10be10 source=17.5 
     <para>
      Fix race condition in handling
      of <varname>synchronous_standby_names</varname> immediately after
      startup (Melnikov Maksim, Michael Paquier)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;3339847cc">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复启动后立即处理
      <varname>synchronous_standby_names</varname> 时的竞态条件（Melnikov Maksim，Michael Paquier）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;3339847cc">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=03eb6141e6353f8a39e5919d1f8287d4 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=f690f8cbc5b1416e6a2f151533c593ef sig_cn_org=36b2ebb171320e4700e4466293e5879a source=17.5 
     <para>
      For a short period after system startup, backends might fail to wait
      for synchronous commit even
      though <varname>synchronous_standby_names</varname> is enabled.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      在系统启动后的短暂时间内，后端可能无法等待同步提交，
      即使启用了<varname>synchronous_standby_names</varname>。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=f690f8cbc5b1416e6a2f151533c593ef -->
    </listitem>

