<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=5ee911947a61095879e63a4121ec5a98 sig_cn_org=3059bdc44cbff3bde2e65f030ce75377 source=17.5 
     <para>
      In <application>pg_amcheck</application>
      and <application>pg_upgrade</application>, use the correct function
      to free allocations made by <application>libpq</application>
      (Michael Paquier, Ranier Vilela)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;ee78823ff">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;0851b6573">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;f903d4da9">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      在<application>pg_amcheck</application>和<application>pg_upgrade</application>中，使用正确的函数释放由
      <application>libpq</application>分配的内存（Michael Paquier，Ranier Vilela）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;ee78823ff">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;0851b6573">&sect;</ulink>
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;f903d4da9">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=5ee911947a61095879e63a4121ec5a98 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=12388b598d6e4d1a83cd004d22cefd95 sig_cn_org=5a364f3654d77f3920be61220d11f2f1 source=17.5 
     <para>
      These oversights could result in crashes in certain Windows build
      configurations, such as a debug build
      of <application>libpq</application> used by a non-debug build of the
      calling application.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      这些疏忽可能导致某些Windows构建配置下的崩溃，例如调试版本的
      <application>libpq</application>被非调试版本的调用应用程序使用时。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=12388b598d6e4d1a83cd004d22cefd95 -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
