<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=7bb0453641887857a9f7a1028df27dd6 sig_cn_org=193f5b7091e2cb7092df8fa65821d68f source=17.5 
     <para>
      Prevent assertion failure
      in <filename>contrib/pg_freespacemap</filename>'s
      <function>pg_freespacemap()</function> (Tender Wang)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;51d038da8">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      防止断言失败
      in <filename>contrib/pg_freespacemap</filename>的
      <function>pg_freespacemap()</function>（Tender Wang）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;51d038da8">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=7bb0453641887857a9f7a1028df27dd6 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=7326725081413d59ae8e7a73620a7e71 sig_cn_org=a281a3be7705683793899053e36d3f64 source=17.5 
     <para>
      Applying <function>pg_freespacemap()</function> to a relation
      lacking storage (such as a view) caused an assertion failure,
      although there was no ill effect in non-assert builds.
      Add an error check to reject that case.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      对于缺少存储（例如视图）的关系，调用<function>pg_freespacemap()</function>会导致断言失败，
      尽管在非断言版本中没有不良影响。添加错误检查以拒绝该情况。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=7326725081413d59ae8e7a73620a7e71 -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
