<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=d13cb10bcbf0e3946d6680a0a71f3de9 sig_cn_org=211d0ad99611842a79ac91b6bf5505df source=17.5 
     <para>
      Update time zone data files to <application>tzdata</application>
      release 2025b for DST law changes in Chile, plus historical
      corrections for Iran (Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;5d5970b9f">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      更新时区数据文件至<application>tzdata</application> 2025b版本，
      以应对智利夏令时法律变更，以及对伊朗的历史修正（Tom Lane）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;5d5970b9f">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=d13cb10bcbf0e3946d6680a0a71f3de9 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=ea6ecaae69a2e7203fa28f77f33058a8 sig_cn_org=6033c739badb31046232a886728a0892 source=17.5 
     <para>
      There is a new time zone America/Coyhaique for Chile's Aysén Region,
      to account for it changing to UTC-03 year-round and thus diverging
      from America/Santiago.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      智利艾森地区新增了一个时区 America/Coyhaique，用以反映该地区全年
      采用 UTC-03 时间，从而与 America/Santiago 时区产生差异。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=ea6ecaae69a2e7203fa28f77f33058a8 -->
    </listitem>

   </itemizedlist>

  </sect2>
 </sect1>

