<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=84738bb79a08fba7c09bb6995d6213cf sig_cn_org=f138927f4b9d470923331de7c0a9ae42 source=17.5 
     <para>
      Fix mis-processing of <function>to_timestamp</function>'s
      <literal>FF<replaceable>n</replaceable></literal> format codes
      (Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;765f76d8c">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复了对<function>to_timestamp</function>的
      <literal>FF<replaceable>n</replaceable></literal>格式代码的错误处理
      （Tom Lane）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;765f76d8c">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=84738bb79a08fba7c09bb6995d6213cf -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=fc9c287203b63a296bf8a7a6e1fdf3d7 sig_cn_org=a32147cc9774711b7b38f52208df2fa5 source=16.8 
     <para>
      An integer format code immediately
      preceding <literal>FF<replaceable>n</replaceable></literal> would
      consume all available digits, leaving none
      for <literal>FF<replaceable>n</replaceable></literal>.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      一个整数格式代码紧接在<literal>FF<replaceable>n</replaceable></literal>
      之前会消耗所有可用的数字，导致<literal>FF<replaceable>n</replaceable></literal>
      没有剩余的数字。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=fc9c287203b63a296bf8a7a6e1fdf3d7 -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
