Branch: REL_15_STABLE [a3b709cf7] 2025-01-14 18:50:24 -0500
Branch: REL_14_STABLE [02e69313a] 2025-01-14 18:50:24 -0500
Branch: REL_13_STABLE [cfd7aadeb] 2025-01-14 18:50:24 -0500
-->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=2a3c301af509b5b028ec8bb635c54309 sig_cn_org=bb82632976207bbe656b71adac3f3d93 source=17.5 
     <para>
      Fix use of wrong version of <function>pqsignal()</function>
      in <application>pgbench</application>
      and <application>psql</application> (Fujii Masao, Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;a0dfeae0d">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修正了在<function>pqsignal()</function>中使用错误版本的问题，
      该问题出现在<application>pgbench</application>和<application>psql</application>中（藤井正雄，汤姆·莱恩）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;a0dfeae0d">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=2a3c301af509b5b028ec8bb635c54309 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=bc0ded1963d17fa43a85c9083fecac06 sig_cn_org=78d0e013a42a7531328f4e0410ce80a8 source=16.8 
     <para>
      This error could lead to misbehavior when using
      the <option>-T</option> option in <application>pgbench</application>
      or the <command>\watch</command> command
      in <application>psql</application>, due to interrupted system calls
      not being resumed as expected.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      此错误可能会导致在使用<option>-T</option>选项时
      的<application>pgbench</application>或<command>\watch</command>
      命令中的<application>psql</application>出现异常行为，
      因为中断的系统调用未按预期恢复。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=bc0ded1963d17fa43a85c9083fecac06 -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
