<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=2d39669cf09c666db2f30f409e7a9a26 sig_cn_org=5cc61de873ccf73cac242acae044da26 source=17.5 
     <para>
      Fix misexecution of some nested <command>\if</command> constructs
      in <application>pgbench</application> (Michail Nikolaev)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;ff9dc96f3">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复了在<command>\if</command>嵌套结构中某些错误执行的问题，
      该问题出现在<application>pgbench</application>中（Michail Nikolaev）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;ff9dc96f3">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=2d39669cf09c666db2f30f409e7a9a26 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b31e8acf3fdd84662bb079301c2ca5fe sig_cn_org=6df0b96abff56f505c34e7101a70b438 source=16.8 
     <para>
      An <command>\if</command> command appearing within a false
      (not-being-executed) <command>\if</command> branch was incorrectly
      treated the same as <command>\elif</command>.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      一个<command>\if</command>命令出现在一个假（未被执行的）
      <command>\if</command>分支中时，被错误地与<command>\elif</command>视为相同。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b31e8acf3fdd84662bb079301c2ca5fe -->
    </listitem>

