Branch: REL_13_STABLE [c24311c1f] 2025-02-05 00:46:06 +0200
-->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=68b1e08ce73e0e0d1bff397396c1b421 sig_cn_org=8df9bea27c2e23e5e4c46e4ba926fde9 source=17.5 
     <para>
      Make <application>pg_controldata</application> more robust against
      corrupted <filename>pg_control</filename> files (Ilyasov Ian, Anton
      Voloshin)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;1b8a9533f">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      使<application>pg_controldata</application>对损坏的<filename>pg_control</filename>文件更具鲁棒性
      （Ilyasov Ian，Anton Voloshin）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;1b8a9533f">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=68b1e08ce73e0e0d1bff397396c1b421 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=79c2ac81a1073d852a97f133b9717c73 sig_cn_org=eb7acd379a612ad7172fa3fbd9eb4e7c source=16.8 
     <para>
      Since <application>pg_controldata</application> will attempt to
      print the contents of <filename>pg_control</filename> even if the
      CRC check fails, it must take care not to misbehave for invalid
      field values.  This patch fixes some issues triggered by invalid
      timestamps and apparently-negative WAL segment sizes.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      由于<application>pg_controldata</application>即使在CRC检查失败时也会尝试
      打印<filename>pg_control</filename>的内容，因此必须注意不要因无效字段值
      而出现异常行为。此补丁修复了一些由无效时间戳和显然为负的WAL段大小
      引发的问题。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=79c2ac81a1073d852a97f133b9717c73 -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
