     <para>
      Fix possible crash in <application>pg_dump</application> with
      identity sequences attached to tables that are extension members
      (Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;ad950ea98">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复了在带有附加到作为扩展成员的表的标识序列时，<application>pg_dump</application>可能崩溃的问题
      （Tom Lane）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;ad950ea98">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=2a170f3bd0695374fe50d765933da276 -->
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
Author: Tom Lane <tgl@sss.pgh.pa.us>
Branch: master [3f0632470] 2024-12-17 22:31:26 -0500
Branch: REL_17_STABLE [04b860198] 2024-12-17 22:31:26 -0500
Branch: REL_16_STABLE [8cfff087b] 2024-12-17 22:31:26 -0500
-->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e191b2f431e52cef2622d6402171174f sig_cn_org=36e5e72f7be9e475a37052860ca5d51a source=17.5 
     <para>
      Fix memory leak in <application>pg_restore</application>
      with zstd-compressed data (Tom Lane)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;04b860198">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      修复了 <application>pg_restore</application> 在处理 zstd 压缩数据时的内存泄漏问题（Tom Lane）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;04b860198">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e191b2f431e52cef2622d6402171174f -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=be3282674d726f1dde8518e9c33ed986 sig_cn_org=c81386eed7dd1df7507970cdeff66959 source=16.8 
     <para>
      The leak was per-decompression-operation, so would be most
      noticeable with a dump containing many tables or large objects.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      该泄漏是每次解压操作发生的，因此在包含许多表或大对象的转储中会最为明显。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=be3282674d726f1dde8518e9c33ed986 -->
    </listitem>

