<!--
Author: Bruce Momjian <bruce@momjian.us>
2023-11-24 [344afc776] modify segno. for pg_walfile_name() and pg_walfile_name_
-->

    <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=089cb2da49b941d3976330eacc010187 sig_cn_org=4ed139a15e9826d7909dc54f34e30252 source=17.5 
     <para>
     Change file boundary handling of two <acronym>WAL</acronym> file
     name functions (Kyotaro Horiguchi, Andres Freund, Bruce Momjian)
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;344afc776">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     更改两个<acronym>WAL</acronym>文件名函数的文件边界处理（Kyotaro Horiguchi, Andres Freund, Bruce Momjian）
     <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;344afc776">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=089cb2da49b941d3976330eacc010187 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=6321f701ab2ca7af6846d24449d4d63b sig_cn_org=5c9c3f97791f4c47519acb8ecd2df835 source=17.5 
     <para>
     The functions <link
     linkend="functions-admin-backup-table"><function>pg_walfile_name()</function></link>
     and <function>pg_walfile_name_offset()</function> used to report
     the previous <acronym>LSN</acronym> segment number when the
     <acronym>LSN</acronym> was on a file segment boundary;  it now
     returns the current <acronym>LSN</acronym> segment.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
     函数 <link
     linkend="functions-admin-backup-table"><function>pg_walfile_name()</function></link>
     和 <function>pg_walfile_name_offset()</function> 过去用于报告
     之前的 <acronym>LSN</acronym> 段号，当 <acronym>LSN</acronym> 位于文件段边界时；
     现在返回当前的 <acronym>LSN</acronym> 段。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=6321f701ab2ca7af6846d24449d4d63b -->
    </listitem>

