Author: Alvaro Herrera <alvherre@alvh.no-ip.org>
2024-02-28 [bcdfa5f2e] Rename SLRU elements in view pg_stat_slru
-->

    <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=d8b1392dee505ab5ce8c7e4f4480fc74 sig_cn_org=564c1d8ca8118e7b1d290ac316644900 source=17.5 
