    <sect4 id="release-17-indexes">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=1dd306ead6471d4aaa831b08d5684b3f sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
     <title>Indexes</title>
________________________________________________________-->
     <title>索引</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=1dd306ead6471d4aaa831b08d5684b3f -->

     <itemizedlist>
<!--
Author: Peter Geoghegan <pg@bowt.ie>
2024-04-06 [5bf748b86] Enhance nbtree ScalarArrayOp execution.
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=f4e5237758b487d204ab0ea12840b90a sig_cn_org=79b9338cd73e5895273f66c243b4d60f source=17.5 
       <para>
       Allow <link linkend="btree">btree</link> indexes to more
       efficiently find a set of values, such as those supplied by
       <literal>IN</literal> clauses using constants (Peter Geoghegan,
       Matthias van de Meent)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;5bf748b86">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       允许<link linkend="btree">btree</link>索引更高效地查找一组值，例如由
       <literal>IN</literal>子句使用常量提供的值（Peter Geoghegan,
       Matthias van de Meent）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;5bf748b86">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=f4e5237758b487d204ab0ea12840b90a -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Tomas Vondra <tomas.vondra@postgresql.org>
2023-12-08 [b43757171] Allow parallel CREATE INDEX for BRIN indexes
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=4218b317600e3ecb6dc5d25ea4e31c34 sig_cn_org=bfd558eb8f1ccf724f0fb7e7aff55849 source=17.5 
       <para>
       Allow <link linkend="brin"><acronym>BRIN</acronym></link> indexes
       to be created using parallel workers (Tomas Vondra, Matthias van
       de Meent)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;b43757171">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       允许使用并行工作线程创建<link linkend="brin"><acronym>BRIN</acronym></link>索引
       （Tomas Vondra，Matthias van de Meent）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;b43757171">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=4218b317600e3ecb6dc5d25ea4e31c34 -->
      </listitem>

     </itemizedlist>

    </sect4>

    <sect4 id="release-17-performance">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=a5864e69d999da12c9d6530175c2c3a6 sig_cn_org=1d8069b437dc11144dd2d5b63a2cffe8 source=15.7 
     <title>General Performance</title>
________________________________________________________-->
     <title>通用性能</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=a5864e69d999da12c9d6530175c2c3a6 -->

     <itemizedlist>

<!--
Author: Heikki Linnakangas <heikki.linnakangas@iki.fi>
2024-04-03 [6dbb49026] Combine freezing and pruning steps in VACUUM
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e40a2b31a203d5514a2d84a104a33270 sig_cn_org=0408449493e64320d89a562875f8e519 source=17.5 
       <para>
       Allow vacuum to more efficiently remove and freeze tuples (Melanie
       Plageman, Heikki Linnakangas)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;6dbb49026">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       允许vacuum更高效地移除和冻结元组（Melanie Plageman，Heikki Linnakangas）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;6dbb49026">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e40a2b31a203d5514a2d84a104a33270 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=587434c677936d3ce658c95d38a38a3c sig_cn_org=587434c677936d3ce658c95d38a38a3c source=17.5 
       <para>
       <acronym>WAL</acronym> traffic caused by vacuum is also more
       compact.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       <acronym>WAL</acronym> traffic caused by vacuum is also more
       compact.
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=587434c677936d3ce658c95d38a38a3c -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: John Naylor <john.naylor@postgresql.org>
2024-03-07 [ee1b30f12] Add template for adaptive radix tree
Author: Masahiko Sawada <msawada@postgresql.org>
2024-03-21 [30e144287] Add TIDStore, to store sets of TIDs (ItemPointerData) ef
Author: Masahiko Sawada <msawada@postgresql.org>
2024-04-02 [667e65aac] Use TidStore for dead tuple TIDs storage during lazy vac
Author: Heikki Linnakangas <heikki.linnakangas@iki.fi>
2024-04-03 [6dbb49026] Combine freezing and pruning steps in VACUUM
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=1ef6fd8c2c2248d52e065b2a6b6d0689 sig_cn_org=2a758602f301db82c675b07195ec728e source=17.5 
       <para>
       Allow vacuum to more efficiently store tuple references (Masahiko
       Sawada, John Naylor)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;ee1b30f12">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;30e144287">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;667e65aac">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;6dbb49026">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       允许真空更高效地存储元组引用（Masahiko Sawada，John Naylor）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;ee1b30f12">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;30e144287">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;667e65aac">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;6dbb49026">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=1ef6fd8c2c2248d52e065b2a6b6d0689 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=3a4712b694f2d1d14d47f0e0892cd931 sig_cn_org=a373c06044566658216376caf2c20d57 source=17.5 
       <para>
       Additionally, vacuum is no longer silently limited to one gigabyte
       of memory when <xref linkend="guc-maintenance-work-mem"/> or <xref
       linkend="guc-autovacuum-work-mem"/> are higher.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       此外，当<xref linkend="guc-maintenance-work-mem"/>或<xref
       linkend="guc-autovacuum-work-mem"/>设置较高时，vacuum不再默默地限制为一
       吉字节内存。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=3a4712b694f2d1d14d47f0e0892cd931 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Robert Haas <rhaas@postgresql.org>
