2023-08-20 [1e68e43d3] Add system view pg_wait_events
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=01979fe341715b4f8877e4af47194cd8 sig_cn_org=2379c015634bc739b3a18c669407c200 source=17.5 
