    <sect4 id="release-17-privileges">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=13cba4791f3b1778f8daa6f35b4036f4 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
     <title>Privileges</title>
________________________________________________________-->
     <title>权限</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=13cba4791f3b1778f8daa6f35b4036f4 -->

     <itemizedlist>

<!--
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2024-03-13 [ecb0fd337] Reintroduce MAINTAIN privilege and pg_maintain predefine
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=7ed25add88912e7a2d033664272eccc7 sig_cn_org=92dd674e68286b73eed2ed83352ca671 source=17.5 
       <para>
       Allow granting the right to perform maintenance operations
       (Nathan Bossart)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;ecb0fd337">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       允许授予执行维护操作的权限
       (Nathan Bossart)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;ecb0fd337">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=7ed25add88912e7a2d033664272eccc7 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b4c1da09553fcd9313b3a72fbe595276 sig_cn_org=c5b6bcc0c5dd2f5b7ec609155643ffb2 source=17.5 
       <para>
       The permission can be granted on a per-table basis using the <link
       linkend="ddl-priv-maintain"><literal>MAINTAIN</literal></link>
       privilege and on a per-role basis via the <link
       linkend="predefined-roles"><literal>pg_maintain</literal></link>
       predefined role.  Permitted operations are
       <command>VACUUM</command>, <command>ANALYZE</command>,
       <command>REINDEX</command>, <command>REFRESH MATERIALIZED
       VIEW</command>, <command>CLUSTER</command>, and <command>LOCK
       TABLE</command>.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       权限可以基于每个表使用<link linkend="ddl-priv-maintain"><literal>MAINTAIN</literal></link>
       权限授予，也可以通过<link linkend="predefined-roles"><literal>pg_maintain</literal></link>
       预定义角色按角色授予。允许的操作包括
       <command>VACUUM</command>、<command>ANALYZE</command>、
       <command>REINDEX</command>、<command>REFRESH MATERIALIZED
       VIEW</command>、<command>CLUSTER</command>和<command>LOCK
       TABLE</command>。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b4c1da09553fcd9313b3a72fbe595276 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Nathan Bossart <nathan@postgresql.org>
2024-02-14 [8d8afd48d] Allow pg_monitor to execute pg_current_logfile().
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=c0981264a191998d97a5fd0ef1aa100c sig_cn_org=4b80aacf612f514d3ac6c5fdc87d541e source=17.5 
       <para>
       Allow roles with <link
       linkend="predefined-roles"><literal>pg_monitor</literal></link>
       membership to execute <link
       linkend="functions-info-session-table"><function>pg_current_logfile()</function></link>
       (Pavlo Golub, Nathan Bossart)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8d8afd48d">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       允许具有<link
       linkend="predefined-roles"><literal>pg_monitor</literal></link>
       角色成员资格执行<link
       linkend="functions-info-session-table"><function>pg_current_logfile()</function></link>
       （Pavlo Golub，Nathan Bossart）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;8d8afd48d">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=c0981264a191998d97a5fd0ef1aa100c -->
      </listitem>

     </itemizedlist>

    </sect4>

