Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2024-04-05 [6f132ed69] Allow synced slots to have their inactive_since.
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=3916bc8734e7a5160f2aaca617f7326e sig_cn_org=a8237aabb23ebc1ab8a4da7dca0f5484 source=17.5 
