    <sect4 id="release-17-logical">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=eb0cc6f28d5a62da9c8aa33738ebd72d sig_cn_org=ebab24a834caa554d1abdf0e8bd252f9 source=15.7 
     <title><link linkend="logical-replication">Logical Replication</link></title>
________________________________________________________-->
     <title><link linkend="logical-replication">逻辑复制</link></title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=eb0cc6f28d5a62da9c8aa33738ebd72d -->

     <itemizedlist>

<!--
Author: Peter Eisentraut <peter@eisentraut.org>
2024-03-25 [d44032d01] pg_createsubscriber: creates a new logical replica from
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=75496844b3bdbac747fabb3b711f9cdc sig_cn_org=e0da4e66ff0f31dcd34fba0532d409fa source=17.5 
       <para>
       Add application <link
       linkend="app-pgcreatesubscriber"><application>pg_createsubscriber</application></link>
       to create a logical replica from a physical standby server
       (Euler Taveira)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d44032d01">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       添加应用程序<link
       linkend="app-pgcreatesubscriber"><application>pg_createsubscriber</application></link>
       用于从物理备用服务器创建逻辑副本
       （Euler Taveira）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;d44032d01">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=75496844b3bdbac747fabb3b711f9cdc -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2023-10-26 [29d0a77fa] Migrate logical slots to the new node during an upgrade.
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2024-01-02 [9a17be1e2] Allow upgrades to preserve the full subscription's state
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e429020c439f350340e52682256e3034 sig_cn_org=9de18c97c4cc95062948d4bea70a5304 source=17.5 
       <para>
       Have <link
       linkend="pgupgrade"><application>pg_upgrade</application></link>
       migrate valid logical slots and subscriptions (Hayato Kuroda,
       Hou Zhijie, Vignesh C, Julien Rouhaud, Shlok Kyal)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;29d0a77fa">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;9a17be1e2">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       让<link
       linkend="pgupgrade"><application>pg_upgrade</application></link>
       迁移有效的逻辑槽和订阅（黑田隼人、侯志杰、Vignesh C、Julien Rouhaud、Shlok Kyal）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;29d0a77fa">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;9a17be1e2">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e429020c439f350340e52682256e3034 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=44c227e3575f4e1713c26189e12d7e9c sig_cn_org=3548b74724d96fea9d723bd227e83932 source=17.5 
       <para>
       This allows logical replication to continue
       quickly after the upgrade.  This only works for old
       <productname>PostgreSQL</productname> clusters that are version
       17 or later.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       这允许逻辑复制在升级后快速继续。此功能仅适用于版本
       17或更高的旧<productname>PostgreSQL</productname>集群。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=44c227e3575f4e1713c26189e12d7e9c -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2024-01-25 [c393308b6] Allow to enable failover property for replication slots
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=844f21163cefd7b81f4ca98a7a3c850c sig_cn_org=924628502b8faa9b6b843c0aeeae0c2b source=17.5 
       <para>
       Enable the failover of <link
       linkend="logical-replication-subscription-slot">logical slots</link>
       (Hou Zhijie, Shveta Malik, Ajin Cherian)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c393308b6">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       启用<link
       linkend="logical-replication-subscription-slot">逻辑槽</link>的故障切换
       （侯志杰，Shveta Malik，Ajin Cherian）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;c393308b6">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=844f21163cefd7b81f4ca98a7a3c850c -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e598176394995c7fa1de86473aa3298d sig_cn_org=2c2bce7f841af325b839459ccb0ab53f source=17.5 
       <para>
       This is controlled by an optional fifth argument to <link
       linkend="functions-replication-table"><function>pg_create_logical_replication_slot()</function></link>.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       这是由一个可选的第五个参数控制，传递给<link
       linkend="functions-replication-table"><function>pg_create_logical_replication_slot()</function></link>。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e598176394995c7fa1de86473aa3298d -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2024-02-22 [93db6cbda] Add a new slot sync worker to synchronize logical slots
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2024-03-06 [60c07820d] Doc: Improve replication slot synchronization section.
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=f095f9de8fbec166ab0f8af2bc22c6b3 sig_cn_org=fa7364e30611f3c935b2adae6df3c526 source=17.5 
       <para>
       Add server variable <xref linkend="guc-sync-replication-slots"/>
       to enable failover logical slot synchronization (Shveta Malik,
       Hou Zhijie, Peter Smith)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;93db6cbda">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;60c07820d">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       添加服务器变量 <xref linkend="guc-sync-replication-slots"/>
       以启用故障转移逻辑槽同步（Shveta Malik,
       侯志杰, Peter Smith）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;93db6cbda">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;60c07820d">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=f095f9de8fbec166ab0f8af2bc22c6b3 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2024-01-30 [776621a5e] Add a failover option to subscriptions.
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2024-02-07 [22f7e61a6] Clean-ups for 776621a5e4 and 7329240437.
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=595b542585b9c79b9edf3a5cab55cb0c sig_cn_org=7bcaedc864cb8bdd72615cb7365b6a1d source=17.5 
       <para>
       Add logical replication failover control to <link
       linkend="sql-createsubscription"><literal>CREATE/ALTER
       SUBSCRIPTION</literal></link> (Shveta Malik, Hou Zhijie, Ajin
       Cherian)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;776621a5e">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;22f7e61a6">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       为<link linkend="sql-createsubscription"><literal>CREATE/ALTER
       SUBSCRIPTION</literal></link>添加逻辑复制故障转移控制（Shveta Malik, 
       Hou Zhijie, Ajin Cherian）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;776621a5e">&sect;</ulink>
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;22f7e61a6">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=595b542585b9c79b9edf3a5cab55cb0c -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2023-07-14 [edca34243] Allow the use of a hash index on the subscriber during r
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=c2f85c5ac408b068211d871f1272030c sig_cn_org=fe82358ca2412a5592083041d7be1eee source=17.5 
       <para>
       Allow the application of logical replication changes to use
       <link linkend="hash-index">hash</link> indexes on the subscriber
       (Hayato Kuroda)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;edca34243">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       允许将逻辑复制更改应用于订阅者上的
       <link linkend="hash-index">哈希</link>索引
       （黑田隼人）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;edca34243">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=c2f85c5ac408b068211d871f1272030c -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=86fefe5293c35a64ee433665d8d5187a sig_cn_org=a5b3d21617e9537513c6dcc44c7f675c source=17.5 
       <para>
       Previously only <link linkend="btree">btree</link> indexes could
       be used for this purpose.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       以前只有<link linkend="btree">btree</link>索引可以用于此目的。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=86fefe5293c35a64ee433665d8d5187a -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Masahiko Sawada <msawada@postgresql.org>
2024-04-03 [5bec1d6bc] Improve eviction algorithm in ReorderBuffer using max-he
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=30dad51ac60dec509c1d7e45442ea4d7 sig_cn_org=f64c5a031368d63d6da9aed9387af73a source=17.5 
       <para>
       Improve <link linkend="logicaldecoding">logical decoding</link>
       performance in cases where there are many subtransactions
       (Masahiko Sawada)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;5bec1d6bc">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       提升<link linkend="logicaldecoding">逻辑解码</link>的性能，尤其是在存在大量子事务的情况下
       （Masahiko Sawada）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;5bec1d6bc">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=30dad51ac60dec509c1d7e45442ea4d7 -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Amit Kapila <akapila@postgresql.org>
2023-10-17 [79243de13] Restart the apply worker if the privileges have been rev
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=eb5d9bc3c348e81da6aeffb888d40553 sig_cn_org=9ead0dd3d288415a31419006ddd80a9c source=17.5 
       <para>
       Restart apply workers if subscription owner's superuser privileges
       are revoked (Vignesh C)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;79243de13">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       如果订阅所有者的超级用户权限被撤销，则重新启动应用工作进程（Vignesh C）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;79243de13">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=eb5d9bc3c348e81da6aeffb888d40553 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=363a2722d3fe93e89bce4cf26ec8f0ce sig_cn_org=395424459c5be9d382c26e343b56370d source=17.5 
       <para>
       This forces reauthentication.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       这会强制重新认证。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=363a2722d3fe93e89bce4cf26ec8f0ce -->
      </listitem>

