Author: Michael Paquier <michael@paquier.xyz>
2023-10-18 [173b56f1e] Add flush option to pg_logical_emit_message()
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=5fe3e83feb276ffc5053b1c6004b753e sig_cn_org=d235b6cc14929a1cb6ccf2eced78d524 source=17.5 
