      <para>
      Allow <link
      linkend="app-pgbasebackup"><application>pg_basebackup</application></link>
      and <link
      linkend="app-pgreceivewal"><application>pg_receivewal</application></link>
      to use dbname in their connection specification (Jelte Fennema-Nio)
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;cca97ce6a">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      允许 <link
      linkend="app-pgbasebackup"><application>pg_basebackup</application></link>
      和 <link
      linkend="app-pgreceivewal"><application>pg_receivewal</application></link>
      在它们的连接规范中使用 dbname（Jelte Fennema-Nio）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;cca97ce6a">&sect;</ulink>
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=8455ff07480c729777948ec17447822f -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=226da96bdf745a47a16a8c7a70e69baf sig_cn_org=cbd9a6a246183886e462a7c3eac45ef7 source=17.5 
      <para>
      This is useful for connection poolers that are sensitive to the
      database name.
      </para>
________________________________________________________-->
      <para>
      这对于对数据库名称敏感的连接池管理器非常有用。
      </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=226da96bdf745a47a16a8c7a70e69baf -->
     </listitem>

