    <sect4 id="release-17-pgstatstatements">
     <title><link linkend="pgstatstatements"><application>pg_stat_statements</application></link></title>

     <itemizedlist>

<!--
Author: Michael Paquier <michael@paquier.xyz>
2023-09-28 [11c34b342] Show parameters of CALL as constants in pg_stat_statemen
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=724d81657f6193ed2048f9b246a5c2ac sig_cn_org=86897fad67f7234c94ac2140da4589d6 source=17.5 
       <para>
       Replace <link linkend="sql-call"><command>CALL</command></link>
       parameters in <application>pg_stat_statements</application> with
       placeholders (Sami Imseih)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;11c34b342">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       替换<application>pg_stat_statements</application> 中的<link linkend="sql-call"><command>CALL</command></link>
       参数为占位符（Sami Imseih）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;11c34b342">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=724d81657f6193ed2048f9b246a5c2ac -->
      </listitem>

<!--
Author: Michael Paquier <michael@paquier.xyz>
2023-07-27 [31de7e60d] Show savepoint names as constants in pg_stat_statements
-->

      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=d54f9ba879925caffd77a86dc8be9728 sig_cn_org=424f3f0acf43d93a255e7d858c9abf31 source=17.5 
       <para>
       Replace savepoint names stored in
       <structname>pg_stat_statements</structname> with placeholders
       (Greg Sabino Mullane)
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;31de7e60d">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       替换存储在
       <structname>pg_stat_statements</structname>中的保存点名称为占位符
       （Greg Sabino Mullane）
       <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;31de7e60d">&sect;</ulink>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=d54f9ba879925caffd77a86dc8be9728 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=770d30741b61ad0cd4614dd232c16c31 sig_cn_org=c4c82752d0a63f7a03e94f3005eed2c1 source=17.5 
       <para>
       This greatly reduces the number of entries needed to record <link
       linkend="sql-savepoint"><command>SAVEPOINT</command></link>,
       <link linkend="sql-release-savepoint"><command>RELEASE
       SAVEPOINT</command></link>, and <link
       linkend="sql-rollback-to"><command>ROLLBACK TO
       SAVEPOINT</command></link> commands.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
       这大大减少了记录<link linkend="sql-savepoint"><command>SAVEPOINT</command></link>、
       <link linkend="sql-release-savepoint"><command>RELEASE SAVEPOINT</command></link>和
       <link linkend="sql-rollback-to"><command>ROLLBACK TO SAVEPOINT</command></link>命令所需的条目数量。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=770d30741b61ad0cd4614dd232c16c31 -->
      </listitem>

